platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Play along with your favourite stars.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 多种风格和乐器 伴你指尖舞蹈

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Not everyone can play like a pro…and that’s OK. Pick a song and Magic Piano does the hard work for you. There’s something for everyone too, from Britney to Beethoven, and as you play you’ll unlock even more great tracks! Some of your favourite artists will even sing along with you as you show the world what you’re made of.
